title: 22: Would the boys be tops or bottoms?
itunes:title: Would the boys be tops or bottoms?
description:
The boys sit down with super funny stand up comedian Thomas Dale (Comedy Central). Trevor and Michael learn about bi-gender, NYC detectives, and if they were gay they definitely would be bottoms. You already guessed that didn’t you. Thomas also brings the guys a very very special surprise. Hint: it’s the name of the podcast.

Want an EXTRA episode a week? Become an exclusive member on Patreon!
